text: Amelia Hudson (born 1903, date of death unknown) was a British diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:Year of death missing Category:British female divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
